OL,3,CMatthew O'Toole breached MLA code of
OL,4,Cconduct by disclosing Lyons complaint
OL,6,FThe SDLP's Stormont leader Matthew
OL,7,FO'Toole breached the MLA's code of
OL,8,Fconduct when he issued a press release
OL,9,Frevealing he had made a complaint
OL,10,Fagainst a DUP minister, a watchdog
OL,11,Freport has found.
OL,13,FFormer independent Assembly
OL,14,FCommissioner for Standards Melissa
OL,15,FMcCullough said Mr O'Toole should have
OL,16,Fknown that making public comment
OL,17,F"concerning an active and confidential
OL,18,Fcomplaint submitted to this office was
OL,19,Finappropriate".
