OL,3,CMatthew O'Toole breached MLA code of
OL,4,Cconduct by disclosing Lyons complaint
OL,6,FNo further action will be taken
OL,7,Fagainst the MLA after he made a
OL,8,Fwritten apology to Stormont's
OL,9,FCommittee on Standards and Privileges.
OL,11,FThe complaint against Mr O'Toole was
OL,12,Fmade after he issued a press release
OL,13,Fin June 2025 disclosing that he had
OL,14,Fsubmitted a formal complaint to the
OL,15,Fcommissioner against Communities
OL,16,FMinister Gordon Lyons.
OL,18,FMr O'Toole's complaint had related to
OL,19,Fcomments made in a social media post
OL,20,Fby Mr Lyons during rioting in Northern
OL,21,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
