OL,3,CMatthew O'Toole breached MLA code of
OL,4,Cconduct by disclosing Lyons complaint
OL,6,FThe commissioner's report concluded
OL,7,Fthat Mr O'Toole had breached Rule 12
OL,8,Fof the code of conduct which states
OL,9,F"You shall disclose confidential or
OL,10,Fprotectively marked information only
OL,11,Fwhen you are authorised to do so."
OL,13,FIn his correspondence with the
OL,14,Fcommissioner, the SDLP MLA pointed out
OL,15,Fthat his press release was issued
OL,16,Fbefore a formal investigation had been
OL,17,Flaunched by her office into Mr Lyons.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@bO]
